    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Tapestry-woven Navajo rugs depicting a center block joined to four corner blocks by zigzag lines, suggesting thunderbolts.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
